Package com.example.mainapplication.datainterface.caching

Class MockCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.mainapplication.datainterface.caching.MockCache
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StorageInterface
    public class MockCache
extends java.lang.Object
implements StorageInterface
    This class is used for testing purposes only. It is a mock cache that returns a list of restaurants and a map of foods. This is used to test the UI without having to connect to the server or without accessing the cache.
    Author:
    Ryan Leska
